   research aimed at better understanding the pollinator attraction
   mechanism of the Neotropical species Vanilla pompona. Based on our
   results, we hypothesize that the identified pollinator Eulaema cingulata
   is attracted via a dual mechanism combining floral fragrance rewards and
   food deception. Abstract in Spanish is available with online material.},
