   Peter, Craig I., Rhodes Univ, Dept Bot, ZA-6140 Grahamstown, South Africa.
   Peter, Craig I.; Johnson, Steven D., Univ KwaZulu Natal, Sch Life Sci, ZA-3209 Scottsville, South Africa.},
