   Oregon State Univ, Dept Forest Sci, Corvallis, OR 97331 USA.
   St Louis Univ, Dept Biol, St Louis, MO 63103 USA.
   US Forest Serv, USDA, Pacific NW Res Stn, Corvallis, OR 97331 USA.},
