   Vallius, Elisa; Salonen, Veikko, Univ Jyvaskyla, Dept Biol \& Environm Sci, Jyvaskyla 40014, Finland.
   Kull, Tiiu, Estonian Univ Life Sci, Inst Agr \& Environm Sci, Dept Bot, EE-51014 Tartu, Estonia.},
