Abstract = {The identity of Polycycnis barbata is discussed and, upon examination of
   the type, the name is lectotypified and synonymized under the species
   with erect, small-flowered inflorescence traditionally known as P.
   muscifera. The large-flowered species of Polycycnis from Costa Rica and
