   Grantham, M. A.; Ford, B. A.; Worley, A. C., Univ Manitoba, Dept Biol Sci, Winnipeg, MB R3T 2N2, Canada.
   Grantham, M. A., Nat Conservancy Canada, Winnipeg, MB R3L 0P3, Canada.},
